<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha"><unclear>sva</unclear>sti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> pukaḻm<unclear>ātu viḷaṅ</unclear>ka <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yamātu virumpa nilamakaḷ nilava malarmakaḷ puṇara Urimaiyiṟ ciṟan=ta maṇimuṭi cūṭi miṉavar nilai <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> kulai <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>riyaluṟ ṟiḻitara tikkaṉaittun taṉ cakkara naṭātti <unclear>vicaiy</unclear>ā<hi rend="grantha">bhi ṣe</hi>kam paṇṇi vira<hi rend="grantha">si-</hi> [ <hi rend="grantha">ṁ hā</hi>] <hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>nattu puvaṉimuḻutuṭaiyāroṭum viṟṟirun=ta ruḷiya
<lb n="3"/>cakkaravarttikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kulottuṅkacoḻatevaṟku yāṇṭu <hi rend="grantha">[<num value="30">3 <g type="numeral">10</g></num>]</hi> Āvatu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ṇṭināṭṭu Uttamacoḻavaḷanāṭṭu kuṭanāṭṭu koṟkaiyāṉa maturān=ta kanallū<unclear>r</unclear>
<lb n="4"/>Akkaicālaiī<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi> ramuṭaiyāṟku Ivvūr veḷāṉ <unclear>na</unclear>mpiṭāraṉeṉ E <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> comaṉāṉa teṉṉavaṉcikāmaṇi muven=ta veḷāṉukku civalokaprārttamāka can=ti rātittavaṟ niro
<lb n="5" break="no"/><supplied reason="omitted">ṭa</supplied>ṭṭik kuṭutta Eṉ pūmi vayakkal taṭi yoṉṟu nilaṅ kāṇikkuṅ kiḷellai <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> comaṉvayakkalukku meṟku n=te ṉṉellai <unclear>Eṉ</unclear> kuṇṭaṟaikku vaṭakku melellai kuṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>ṅki comaṉvayakkalukku kiḷakkum vaṭavellai Araiyaṉvaca <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> kku teṟkum Innāṉkellaik kuṭpaṭṭa nilaṅ kāṇiyum can=ti rātittavaṟ niroṭaṭṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>veṭṭikkuṭutteṉ veḷāṉ nampiṭāraṉeṉ <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> meṟpaṭi<unclear>yūr</unclear><note n="244-2">The inscription is damaged.</note> 
